value.name: Michelangelo Towers - Wikipedia
value.snippet: The Michelangelo Towers is a hotel building in Sandton, South Africa. It is a prominent structure in the Sandton skyline and is one of South Africa's elite hotels, having accommodated guests such as former United States President Barack Obama , Oprah Winfrey , Angelina Jolie , Mariah Carey , Paris Hilton , Kanye West , Lady Gaga and Justin Bieber .

value.name: Michelangelo Towers | Legacy Hotels & Resorts
value.snippet: Located on Nelson Mandela Square, in the heart of Sandton, The Michelangelo Towers offers the finest collection of executive 1 and 2 bedroom rental apartments, for either short or long term stays. With direct access to the Sandton Convention Centre, Sandton City and the Gautrain, The Michelangelo Towers is the ideal location for your business needs.
